      <title>TikTok 瞄准亚马逊 175 亿美元的购物业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/tiktok-eyes-17-5-billion-shopping-business-on-amazon-s-turf</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，字节跳动旗下 TikTok 的目标是今年将其美国电子商务业务规模扩大十倍，达到 175 亿美元，这对亚马逊公司构成更大的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/tiktok-eyes-17-5-billion-shopping-business-on-amazon-s-turf</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 23:03:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>扎克伯格在过去两个月出售了近 5 亿美元的 Meta 股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/zuckerberg-sold-nearly-half-a-billion-dollars-of-meta-stock-in-last-two-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·扎克伯格 (Mark Zuckerberg) 在 2023 年最后两个月出售了近 5 亿美元的 Meta Platforms Inc. 股票，此前该公司股价跌至七年来的最低点，两年间中断了该股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/zuckerberg-sold-nearly-half-a-billion-dollars-of-meta-stock-in-last-two-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 22:55:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔任命外部人士霍塔德领导关键数据中心部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/intel-appoints-outsider-hotard-to-head-crucial-data-center-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司任命惠普企业公司高管贾斯汀·霍塔德（Justin Hotard）领导其数据中心和人工智能部门，并聘请外部人士来管理对芯片制造商扭亏为盈至关重要的部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/intel-appoints-outsider-hotard-to-head-crucial-data-center-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 21:50:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迪士尼挑战佩尔茨，比特币逆转进程彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-03/bloomberg-technology-01-03-2024-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的卡罗琳·海德 (Caroline Hyde) 和埃德·勒德洛 (Ed Ludlow) 详细分析了迪士尼与激进分子纳尔逊·佩尔茨 (Nelson Peltz) 的斗争，因为迪士尼赢得了 ValueAct Capital 对其董事会提名人的支持。此外，由于 SEC 的 ETF 决定仍存在不确定性，比特币抹去了今年的涨幅。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-03/bloomberg-technology-01-03-2024-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 21:24:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大宽带公司 Xplore 正在洽谈获得新融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/canada-broadband-firm-xplore-in-talks-to-receive-fresh-money</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，为农村社区提供高速互联网服务的 Xplore Inc. 计划通过将资产转移到新的法人实体并以这些实体为抵押进行借贷来筹集新的融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/canada-broadband-firm-xplore-in-talks-to-receive-fresh-money</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 20:13:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
