    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉在多次降价后减少了对租赁的依赖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/tesla-relies-on-leasing-less-after-repeatedly-slashing-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司季度销售额的一小部分依赖租赁，一位分析师表示，这一趋势可能与疲软的转售价值有关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/tesla-relies-on-leasing-less-after-repeatedly-slashing-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 17:43:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
